---
title: Thai-Style Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Salad with Ginger Dressing & Peanuts
description: Make way for this hearty main meal salad in your dinner rotation. With mildly spiced chicken and a fragrant ginger dressing, this plate of bountiful greens and pumpkin will change the way you look at veggies!
